author: Hannah (Sensational Sidekick)
title: JetBlue Airlines: Select One-Way Flights Starting at $20
text:
Looking to get out of town? For a limited time and while supplies last, JetBlue is hosting a flash sale and offering up flights starting at just $20 for select dates! Note that flight dates will vary anywhere from February 25th-March 8th. As a deal idea, you can book a ticket from Washington, D.C. to Orlando, Florida for just $30!

Check out these Five Ways to Save BIG on Travel! (Thanks, Leah!)
